    "Thanks to recent advances in deep learning, the performance of natural language processing applications has been improved in an unprecedented way, attracting increasing interest from the machine learning community (Kotsiantis et al. 2006).",
    "For example, the most (Wang et al. 2021a) advanced phrase-based statistical methods in machine translation have been gradually replaced by neural machine translation (Yadav and Vishwakarma 2020).",
    "Neural machine translation involves large deep neural networks that achieve better performance (Bahdanau et al. 2014).",
